body_html:
Does accessing tf.contrib on windows still work with this change?

(in the change that enabled nccl in cmake, it was also imported by contrib/init.py - and that import may fail now if the op library can't be loaded).

body:
Does accessing tf.contrib on windows still work with this change?

(in the change that enabled nccl in cmake, it was also imported by contrib/__init__.py - and that import may fail now if the op library can't be loaded).
